        depends on ULTRASONIC_NORMAL_MODE
        default 200 if IDF_TARGET_ESP32 || IDF_TARGET_ESP32S2 || IDF_TARGET_ESP32S3
        help
            Maximum measurable distance. If the distance is greater than this parameter, there will be a timeout
